title: BRIEF-Alcatel-Lucent and BT commence G.fast ultra-broadband access technology trial
text:
Oct 9 Alcatel-Lucent SA :
* Commences together with BT an extensive trial of G.fast ultra-broadband access technology in north-east England Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
